OL,6,FA Bristol lecturer who survived stage
OL,7,F4 cancer thanks to a stem cell
OL,8,Ftransplant is running the London
OL,9,FMarathon to help others in need.
OL,11,FAfter a year of punishing cancer
OL,12,Ftreatment, Dr Yani Berdeni could
OL,13,Fbarely walk.
OL,15,FBut two-and-a-half years on from
OL,16,Fgetting the all-clear, he is ready to
OL,17,Ftake on the 26.2-mile course.
