OL,6,FThe University of Bristol engineering
OL,7,Fmaths lecturer was 30-years-old when a
OL,8,Fpersistent cough was diagnosed as
OL,9,Flymphoma, a type of blood cancer that
OL,10,Faffects the immune system.
OL,12,FThe diagnosis came just a few days
OL,13,Fbefore Christmas 2019.
OL,15,FFour rounds of chemotherapy and
OL,16,Fradiotherapy followed, and the
OL,17,Fprognosis looked bright.
