OL,6,FBut in summer 2020 new and
OL,7,F"excruciating" back pain turned out to
OL,8,Fbe a large cancerous tumour squeezing
OL,9,Fhis spine.
OL,11,F"The whole experience was surreal `
OL,12,Fyou just don't expect it at 30. But
OL,13,Ffinding out about the stage 4 cancer
OL,14,Fwas the hardest thing," Dr Berdeni
OL,15,Fsaid.
