OL,3,CCancer survivor who could barely walk
OL,4,Cnow running to help others
OL,6,F"I needed a stem cell transplant and
OL,7,Fwas told it only had a 50% success
OL,8,Frate. They took my stem cells and then
OL,9,Fgave me so much chemo that I would've
OL,10,Fdied, but then they injected the cells
OL,11,Fback into my blood to regrow the bone
OL,12,Fmarrow."
OL,14,FThe treatment made Dr Berdeni so weak
OL,15,Fthat a cold could have killed him.
OL,16,FWith Covid still raging, his partner,
OL,17,FRuby Hodgson, would read him books via
OL,18,Fvideo call.
