OL,3,CCancer survivor who could barely walk
OL,4,Cnow running to help others
OL,6,FIn July 2021, he was given the all-
OL,7,Fclear. Not long afterwards he was made
OL,8,Fa lecturer at the University of
OL,9,FBristol, where he had been studying
OL,10,Fand working since 2012.
OL,12,FDr Berdeni was a keen runner before
OL,13,Fhis diagnosis, and entered the London
OL,14,FMarathon in 2013.
OL,16,FHe was heading towards an impressive
OL,17,Fsub-three hour time when he collapsed
OL,18,F800 metres from the end.
