OL,4,Cnow running to help others
OL,6,F"When I came round I thought I was in
OL,7,FBradford, where I grew up," Dr Berdeni
OL,8,Fsaid.
OL,10,F"So, yeah, I've got unfinished
OL,11,Fbusiness at the London Marathon."
OL,13,FDr Berdeni, now 34, is raising money
OL,14,Ffor the "amazing" blood cancer charity
OL,15,FAnthony Nolan, which runs a stem cell
OL,16,Fdonor register and carries out
OL,17,Fresearch into the disease.
OL,19,F"After the treatment I could barely
OL,20,Fwalk," he said.
