OL,3,CCancer survivor who could barely walk
OL,4,Cnow running to help others
OL,6,F"I was 10kg heavier because of
OL,7,Fbloating from the treatment and I
OL,8,Fwould jog for 500 metres and be
OL,9,Fexhausted. I just wanted to get back
OL,10,Fto feeling healthy and normal again."
OL,12,FDr Berdeni was helped back into
OL,13,Frunning by 5k Your Way, an inclusive
OL,14,Frunning community that helps those
OL,15,Faffected by cancer.
OL,17,FMs Hodgson and other friends and
OL,18,Ffamily members will be waiting at the
OL,19,FLondon Marathon finish line on April
OL,20,F21.
