OL,6,F"It will be quite emotional and a bit
OL,7,Foverwhelming," Dr Berdeni said.
OL,9,F"I really just want to make it round
OL,10,Fand raise money for Anthony Nolan.
OL,11,FThey need donors under 30 and you
OL,12,Freally could save someone's life. If
OL,13,Fmy cancer came back, I would need to
OL,14,Fuse someone else's stem cells."
OL,16,FDr Berdeni has set up a JustGiving
OL,17,Fpage .
